    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/5807b9b437568f35894fd4d4fcf62168.avif?t=1736824332\" width=616 height=79 /></span><br><br>欢迎来到《DADOO》的疯狂混乱惊奇世界——这款游戏是对传统蛇梯棋游戏的深度改造与创新，绝对让你认不出本来的模样！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/943c1faaf6790a189f7815e9e08389cc.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/943c1faaf6790a189f7815e9e08389cc.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/943c1faaf6790a189f7815e9e08389cc.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这不是一般的多人在线游戏，这是考验你战略思维的无规则战场。千万不要只仰仗运气，而且你能相信的人只有你自己。不过记住了，这款游戏的制胜规则仅仅只有抵达终点而已。享受这旅途吧，让混乱展开，同时也别忘了折磨你的对手。<br><br>那么，你还在等什么呢？掷出骰子，打出卡牌，邀请你的好友一同潜入史诗般的大混乱，只要能确保你们玩完一局《DADOO：阴谋诡计，惊天反转》之后，你们还是好朋友就好了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/35c8173428f9e268468c26e71157061e.avif?t=1736824332\" width=616 height=79 /></span><br><br><strong>1.这里会有蛇。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/bd3e4849f4f1b9a14e4031e4a0b14769.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/bd3e4849f4f1b9a14e4031e4a0b14769.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/bd3e4849f4f1b9a14e4031e4a0b14769.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2.这里会有梯子（不过在这张动图里是加农炮）。 </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/b71dcacfad4205a1c9c38ede4c7d8b69.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/b71dcacfad4205a1c9c38ede4c7d8b69.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/b71dcacfad4205a1c9c38ede4c7d8b69.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3.超过20张超强卡牌可以让你用来碾压对手（或者保护自己！）</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/51f99587c10cfa2f4fc9dfb7e61443d3.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/51f99587c10cfa2f4fc9dfb7e61443d3.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/51f99587c10cfa2f4fc9dfb7e61443d3.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4.跨平台多人游戏！可以和你在PC和安卓手机上的朋友一起游戏。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/a3f7c0f4c273bd3ec5a8795050ad342c.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/a3f7c0f4c273bd3ec5a8795050ad342c.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/a3f7c0f4c273bd3ec5a8795050ad342c.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>5.支持多种语言，包括英语、印尼语、葡萄牙语、韩语、日语。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/ab997f2bd8869be4a999a348c4a453d0.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/ab997f2bd8869be4a999a348c4a453d0.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/ab997f2bd8869be4a999a348c4a453d0.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>6.超多可爱的吉祥物角色供你选择。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/8ea3e5ad5235806144aa901c1729dbd1.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/8ea3e5ad5235806144aa901c1729dbd1.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/8ea3e5ad5235806144aa901c1729dbd1.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>7.嘿，每个角色都还有自己独特的超能力哟。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/2184721b659da4044258c7fe8c3f139b.poster.avif?t=1736824332\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/2184721b659da4044258c7fe8c3f139b.webm?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230290/extras/2184721b659da4044258c7fe8c3f139b.mp4?t=1736824332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>购买Steam版本的《Dadoo》即可领取独占奖励！独特全新卡牌和皮肤等你来拿。</strong>",
